               <t:note>
                  <t:date type="foundation" notBefore="1400" notAfter="1500">1400-1500</t:date>
                  <t:desc type="foundation">The church is said to be old; the monastic community (now extinct) was established by <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8265Sabagadi">Dağğāzmāč Sabāgādis</t:persName> (1780-1831).</t:desc>
                  <t:ab type="history">Gaṭar. Two churches are at the site; one is very recent, one is older (but not older than 19th cent.); some unidentified structures are in the rock above the older church.
</t:ab>
                  <t:ab type="description">
                     
                     <t:figure>
